# =============================================================================
# Nutri Beta Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
#
# This file documents environment variables for the BETA environment.
# Beta is used for testing before production deployment.
#
# For mobile app builds:
#   - Set these in EAS secrets or as environment variables
#   - Beta builds can be distributed via TestFlight/Internal Testing
#
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# API Configuration (Beta)
# =============================================================================

# Beta API URL - points to beta backend instance
# This should be set in EAS secrets for beta builds
BETA_API_URL=https://beta-api.yourapp.com/api

# Override for development testing against beta
# API_URL=https://beta-api.yourapp.com/api

# =============================================================================
# GitHub Actions Secrets Required for Beta Deployment
# =============================================================================
#
# Set these in your GitHub repository secrets:
#
# Database:
#   BETA_DATABASE_URL     - PostgreSQL connection string for beta database
#   BETA_DIRECT_URL       - Direct connection for Prisma migrations (optional)
#
# Coolify Webhooks:
#   COOLIFY_BETA_BACKEND_WEBHOOK_URL  - Webhook URL for beta backend deployment
#   COOLIFY_BETA_ML_WEBHOOK_URL       - Webhook URL for beta ML service deployment
#   COOLIFY_WEBHOOK_SECRET            - Shared webhook secret (same as production)
#
# Health Check:
#   BETA_API_URL          - Public URL to beta API for health checks
#
# =============================================================================
